---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Accessibility — Community Starter"
  description="Community Starter accessibility commitment."
>
  <article class="page-heading reading cs-shell">
    <p class="cs-eyebrow">Accessibility</p>
    <h1>Community includes how people access it.</h1>
    <p>
      Community Starter targets WCAG 2.2 AA, supports keyboard use, reflow,
      reduced motion, and assistive technology, and treats accessibility
      failures as product defects.
    </p>
    <p>
      To report a barrier, use the support contact configured for this
      deployment.
    </p>
  </article>
</SiteLayout>
